The paper deals with bandit learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and falls under the category of "cs.LG" (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses regret analysis, which is a common topic in reinforcement learning, another subfield of machine learning. Therefore, "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence) is also a likely category. The paper also proposes a new algorithm and establishes a regret bound, which involves mathematical analysis and optimization, making "cs.DS" (Data Structures and Algorithms) and "cs.IT" (Information Theory) possible categories. Finally, the paper deals with decision-making under time preference, which is a topic in control theory, making "cs.SY" (Systems and Control) a possible category as well.
